Package: abbyyR
Title: R CLIENT TO ABBYY FINEREADER CLOUD OCR SDK API 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Gaurav", "Sood", email = "gsood07@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides easy access to the Abbyy FineReader Cloud OCR API. A variety of functions to process a wide variety of image formats is implemented including ability to OCR businessCards, text fields from surveys among other features.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL v3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Author: Gaurav Sood <gsood07@gmail.com> [aut, cre]
